\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><img alt=\\\"iphone-8-1575014439.jpg\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/lapvip.vn\\/upload\\/file\\/thumb_800x0\\/iphone-8-1575014439.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">B\\u1ea1n s\\u1ebd th\\u1ea5y s\\u1ef1 xu\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n c\\u1ee7a l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ed1i. Ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 t\\u1ed1i trong iOS 13 c&oacute; giao di\\u1ec7n t\\u1ed1i nh\\u1ea1t h\\u01a1i n&acirc;u, kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; g\\u1eaft nh\\u01b0 ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ed1i c\\u1ee7a Facebook v&agrave; nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nhi\\u1ec1u l\\u1eddi khen.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><img alt=\\\"iphone-7-1575014455.jpg\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/lapvip.vn\\/upload\\/file\\/thumb_800x0\\/iphone-7-1575014455.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">N\\u1ec1n \\u0111en nh\\u01b0ng c&aacute;c ph&ocirc;ng ch\\u1eef c&oacute; m&agrave;u tr\\u1eafng, t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 c&aacute;c t&ugrave;y ch\\u1ecdn c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 nh\\u1ea5n ho\\u1eb7c ch\\u1ecdn v\\u0103n b\\u1ea3n c&oacute; m&agrave;u xanh c\\u1ed5 \\u0111i\\u1ec3n.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3 style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><strong>2. B\\u1eadt ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ed1i trong trung t&acirc;m \\u0111i\\u1ec1u khi\\u1ec3n<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">Ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng v\\u1eabn c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 b\\u1eadt nhanh ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ed1i t\\u1ea1i Trung t&acirc;m \\u0111i\\u1ec1u khi\\u1ec3n. \\u0110\\u1ec3 b\\u1eadt ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ed1i, c&aacute;c b\\u1ea1n h&atilde;y v&agrave;o&nbsp;<em><strong>c&agrave;i \\u0111\\u1eb7t<\\/strong><\\/em>&nbsp;v&agrave; nh\\u1ea5n ch\\u1ea1m v&agrave;o&nbsp;<em>t<strong>&ugrave;y ch\\u1ec9nh \\u0111i\\u1ec1u khi\\u1ec3n<\\/strong><\\/em>.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><img alt=\\\"C\\u00e1ch k\\u00edch ho\\u1ea1t ch\\u1ebf \\u0111