es=\\\"\\\" data-src=\\\"\\/\\/thinkpro.vn\\/uploads\\/images\\/userfiles\\/dell_precision_7720_10.jpg\\\" data-srcset=\\\"\\\" data-style=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/thinkpro.vn\\/uploads\\/images\\/userfiles\\/dell_precision_7720_10.jpg\\\" srcset=\\\"\\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><em>B&agrave;n ph&iacute;m Precision 7720<\\/em><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><strong>&Acirc;M THANH<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">Loa c\\u1ee7a m&aacute;y c&oacute; &acirc;m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng l\\u1edbn, ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng &acirc;m r\\u1ea5t t\\u1ed1t. D\\u1ea3i &acirc;m bass m\\u1ea1nh v&agrave; s\\u1eafc n&eacute;t. b\\u1ea1n c\\u0169ng c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ch\\u1ec9nh &acirc;m thanh theo &yacute; m&igrave;nh b\\u1eb1ng c&aacute;ch ch\\u1ec9nh c&agrave;i \\u0111\\u1eb7t trong ti\\u1ec7n &iacute;ch &acirc;m thanh Waves MaxxAudio Pro.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><strong>HI\\u1ec6U N\\u0102NG&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">\\u0110\\u01b0\\u1ee3c trang b\\u1ecb vi x\\u1eed l&yacute; Intel Xeon E3-1535M v6 , 8GB RAM, \\u0111\\u1ed3 ho\\u1ea1 Nvidia Quadro P3000 v&agrave; m\\u1ed9t SSD PCIe Class 40 256GB, c\\