 thu\\u1ed9c d&ograve;ng workstation di \\u0111\\u1ed9ng th\\u1ebf h\\u1ec7 m\\u1edbi c\\u1ee7a Dell ch&iacute;nh th\\u1ee9c ra m\\u1eaft ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng v&agrave;o cu\\u1ed1i n\\u0103m ngo&aacute;i v&agrave; \\u0111&acirc;y c\\u0169ng l&agrave; phi&ecirc;n b\\u1ea3n thay th\\u1ebf cho M6800 tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111&acirc;y. S\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m kh&ocirc;ng ch\\u1ec9 c&oacute; thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf m\\u1ecfng nh\\u1eb9, nhi\\u1ec1u t&ugrave;y ch\\u1ecdn c\\u1ea5u h&igrave;nh m\\u1ea1nh h\\u01a1n m&agrave; c&ograve;n c&oacute; th\\u1eddi l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng d&ugrave;ng pin t\\u1ed1t h\\u01a1n \\u0111&aacute;ng k\\u1ec3, \\u0111\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ebfn 16 gi\\u1edd li&ecirc;n t\\u1ee5c v\\u1edbi pin c&ocirc;ng su\\u1ea5t l\\u1edbn.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><strong>THI\\u1ebeT K\\u1ebe B\\u1ec0N B\\u1ec8, S&Aacute;NG T\\u1ea0O<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">S\\u1ef1 thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 nh\\u1eadn th\\u1ea5y v\\u1ec1 ki\\u1ec3u d&aacute;ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m l&agrave; m\\u1ecfng nh\\u1eb9 h\\u01a1n so phi&ecirc;n b\\u1ea3n M4800 v\\u1edbi c&aacute;c &ldquo;s\\u1ed1 \\u0111o&rdquo; 37,8 x 26,1 x 2,78 cm v&agrave; n\\u1eb7ng 3.2 kg. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n n\\u1ebfu so v\\u1edbi c&aacute;c laptop d&ograve;ng ph\\u1ed5 th&ocirc;ng th&igrave; Precision 7720 v\\u1eabn ch\\u01b0a b\\u1eaft k\\u1ecbp \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c xu h\\u01b0\\u1edbng m\\u1ecfng nh\\u1eb9 hi\\u1ec7n nay.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><img alt=\\\"dell-precision-7720-lapvip-1575688826.jpg\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/lapvip.vn\\/upload\\/file\\/thumb_800x0\\/dell-precision-7720-lapvip-1575688826.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">V\\u1edbi tr\\u1ecdng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng 3.2&nbsp;kg v&agrave; d&agrave;y 3.5 cm,&nbsp;<strong>Dell Precision<\\/strong>&nbsp;7720 c&oacute; k&iacute;ch th\\u01b0\\u1edbc kh&aacute; gi\\u1ed1ng nh\\u1eefng d&ograve;ng laptop Workstation m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh 17.3 inch kh&aacute;c nh\\u01b0&nbsp;<strong>Lenovo Thinkpad<\\/strong>&nbsp;P70 hay&nbsp;<strong>Zbook Studio<\\/strong>&nbsp;G4. Tuy r\\u1eb1ng m&aacute;y kh&aacute; to v&agrave; n\\u1eb7ng nh\\u01b0ng v\\u1eabn cho c\\u1ea3m gi&aacute;c h\\u1ebft s\\u1ee9c tho\\u1ea3i m&aacute;i khi ch\\u1ea1m v&agrave;o. N\\u1eafp m&aacute;y l&agrave;m t\\u1eeb s\\u1ee3i Carbon v&agrave; b&agrave;n ph&iacute;m m\\u1ec1m m\\u1ea1i cho c\\u1ea3m gi&aacute;c tuy\\u1ec7t v\\u1eddi gi&uacute;p m&aacute;y c&oacute; tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m t\\u1ed5ng th\\u1ec3 t\\u1ed1t h\\u01a1n.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><strong>\\u0110\\u1ed8 B\\u1ec0N V&Agrave;&nbsp;AN NINH C\\u1ef0C T\\u1ed0T<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">Precision 7720 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u1ea1i nh\\u1eefng va \\u0111\\u1eadp khi di chuy\\u1ec3n. Theo Dell, Precision 7720 \\u0111&atilde; v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t qua 15 b&agrave;i ki\\u1ec3m tra \\u0111\\u1ed9 b\\u1ec1n MIL-SPEC, bao g\\u1ed3m nhi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed9, n\\u1ed5 c&aacute;t, va \\u0111\\u1eadp v&agrave; r\\u01a1i t\\u1ef1 do.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">V\\u1ec1 an ninh, m&aacute;y c&oacute; ti&ecirc;u chu\\u1ea9n v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ea7u \\u0111\\u1ecdc th\\u1ebb th&ocirc;ng minh v&agrave; m&atilde; h&oacute;a TPM. B\\u1ea1n c\\u0169ng c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn phi&ecirc;n b\\u1ea3n c&oacute; \\u0111\\u1ea7u \\u0111\\u1ecdc d\\u1ea5u v&acirc;n tay ho\\u1eb7c b\\u1ed9 c\\u1ea3m bi\\u1ebfn NFC. N\\u1ebfu b\\u1ea1n thi\\u1ebft l\\u1eadp c\\u1ea5u h&igrave;nh m&aacute;y v\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9t CPU t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng th&iacute;ch, n&oacute; c\\u0169ng s\\u1ebd c&oacute; c&ocirc;ng ngh\\u1ec7 qu\\u1ea3n l&yacute; t\\u1eeb xa vPro c\\u1ee7a Intel.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><strong>C\\u1ed4NG K\\u1ebeT N\\u1ed0I<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><img alt=\\\"c\\u1ea1nh tr\\u00e1i Precision 7720\\\" data-l=\\\"\\\" data-sizes=\\\"\\\" data-src=\\\"\\/\\/thinkpro.vn\\/uploads\\/images\\/userfiles\\/dell_precision_7720_4.jpg\\\" data-srcset=\\\"\\\" data-style=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/thinkpro.vn\\/uploads\\/images\\/userfiles\\/dell_precision_7720_4.jpg\\\" srcset=\\\"\\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">B&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i l&agrave; m\\u1ed9t c\\u1ed5ng USB 3.0, m\\u1ed9t c\\u1ed5ng Thunderbolt 3 , c\\u1ed5ng HDMI, m\\u1ed9t DisplayPort mini v&agrave; m\\u1ed9t \\u0111\\u1ea7u \\u0111\\u1ecdc th\\u1ebb th&ocirc;ng minh.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><img alt=\\\"c\\u1ea1nh ph\\u1ea3i Precision 7720\\\" data-l=\\\"\\\" data-sizes=\\\"\\\" data-src=\\\"\\/\\/thinkpro.vn\\/uploads\\/images\\/userfiles\\/dell_precision_7720_8.jpg\\\" data-srcset=\\\"\\\" data-style=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/thinkpro.vn\\/uploads\\/images\\/userfiles\\/dell_precision_7720_8.jpg\\\" srcset=\\\"\\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">B&ecirc;n ph\\u1ea3i c&oacute; ba c\\u1ed5ng USB 3.0, m\\u1ed9t l\\u1ed7 c\\u1eafm tai nghe, m\\u1ed9t \\u1ed5 kh&oacute;a an to&agrave;n v&agrave; m\\u1ed9t \\u0111\\u1ea7u \\u0111\\u1ecdc th\\u1ebb SD. C\\u1ed5ng m\\u1ea1ng LAN v&agrave; ngu\\u1ed3n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u1eb7t \\u1edf c\\u1ea1nh sau.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><strong>M&Agrave;N H&Igrave;NH \\u0110\\u1eb8P R\\u1ef0C R\\u1ee0<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh c\\u1ee7a Dell Precision 7720 m&agrave; m&igrave;nh \\u0111ang s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 review \\u1edf \\u0111&acirc;y c&oacute; \\u0111\\u1ed9 ph&acirc;n gi\\u1ea3i Full HD (1920 x 1080 pixel), cho m&agrave;u s\\u1eafc r\\u1ef1c r&otilde; v&agrave; chi ti\\u1ebft s\\u1eafc n&eacute;t. M&agrave;u s\\u1eafc hi\\u1ec3n th\\u1ecb ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c, tr&ecirc;n th\\u1eed nghi\\u1ec7m Delta-E ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng sai c\\u1ee7a m&aacute;y ch\\u1ec9 l&agrave; 0.3, th\\u1ea5p h\\u01a1n so v\\u1edbi m\\u1ee9c trung b&igrave;nh c\\u1ee7a PC l&agrave; 1.5, hay nh\\u1eefng chi\\u1ebfc laptop nh\\u01b0 Zbook Studio (2,4), ThinkPad P70 (0,7 ) V&agrave; Precision 5520 (1,5).<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><img alt=\\\"dell-precision-7720-lapvip-1575688718.jpg\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/lapvip.vn\\/upload\\/file\\/thumb_800x0\\/dell-precision-7720-lapvip-1575688718.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><em>M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh Precision 7720<\\/em><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh c\\u1ee7a Precision 7720 c&oacute; \\u0111\\u1ed9 s&aacute;ng 317 nits, h\\u01a1n m\\u1ee9c trung b&igrave;nh l&agrave; 290 nits. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n&nbsp;m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh n&agrave;y l\\u1ea1i kh&ocirc;ng gi\\u1eef \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c m&agrave;u s\\u1eafc khi nh&igrave;n \\u1edf 45 \\u0111\\u1ed9 nghi&ecirc;ng sang tr&aacute;i ho\\u1eb7c ph\\u1ea3i.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><strong>B&Agrave;N PH&Iacute;M v&agrave; TOUCHPAD TUY\\u1ec6T V\\u1edcI<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">B&agrave;n ph&iacute;m c\\u1ee7a Dell Precision \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf c\\u1ef1c k&igrave; thu\\u1eadn ti\\u1ec7n cho vi\\u1ec7c nh\\u1eadp li\\u1ec7u v&agrave; ch\\u1ec9nh s\\u1eeda v\\u0103n b\\u1ea3n. H&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh ph&iacute;m l&agrave; 1.8mm v&agrave; l\\u1ef1c \\u1ea5n l&agrave; 69 gram, b&agrave;n ph&iacute;m cho c\\u1ea3m gi&aacute;c tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m s&acirc;u v&agrave; t\\u1ed1t.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">Touchpad c\\u1ee7a m&aacute;y c&oacute; k&iacute;ch th\\u01b0\\u1edbc 3.9&times;2 inch \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf c&oacute; 2 b\\u1ed9 chu\\u1ed9t tr&ecirc;n v&agrave; d\\u01b0\\u1edbi c&oacute; c\\u1ea3m gi&aacute;c b\\u1ea5m ch\\u1eafc ch\\u1eafn v&agrave; r\\u1ea5t ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c. \\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi touchpad c\\u1ee7a precision cho phaes \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7 c&aacute;c thao t&aacute;c \\u0111a \\u0111i\\u1ec3m tr&ecirc;n windows 10.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><img alt=\\\"b\\u00e0n ph\\u00edm Precision 7720\\\" data-l=\\\"\\\" data-sizes=\\\"\\\" data-src=\\\"\\/\\/thinkpro.vn\\/uploads\\/images\\/userfiles\\/dell_precision_7720_10.jpg\\\" data-srcset=\\\"\\\" data-style=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/thinkpro.vn\\/uploads\\/images\\/userfiles\\/dell_precision_7720_10.jpg\\\" srcset=\\\"\\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><em>B&agrave;n ph&iacute;m Precision 7720<\\/em><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><strong>&Acirc;M THANH<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">Loa c\\u1ee7a m&aacute;y c&oacute; &acirc;m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng l\\u1edbn, ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng &acirc;m r\\u1ea5t t\\u1ed1t. D\\u1ea3i &acirc;m bass m\\u1ea1nh v&agrave; s\\u1eafc n&eacute;t. b\\u1ea1n c\\u0169ng c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ch\\u1ec9nh &acirc;m thanh theo &yacute; m&igrave;nh b\\u1eb1ng c&aacute;ch ch\\u1ec9nh c&agrave;i \\u0111\\u1eb7t trong ti\\u1ec7n &iacute;ch &acirc;m thanh Waves MaxxAudio Pro.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><strong>HI\\u1ec6U N\\u0102NG&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">\\u0110\\u01b0\\u1ee3c trang b\\u1ecb vi x\\u1eed l&yacute; Intel Xeon E3-1535M v6 , 8GB RAM, \\u0111\\u1ed3 ho\\u1ea1 Nvidia Quadro P3000 v&agrave; m\\u1ed9t SSD PCIe Class 40 256GB, c\\u1ea5u h&igrave;nh xem l\\u1ea1i c\\u1ee7a Precision 7720 l&agrave;&nbsp;\\u0111\\u1ee7 s\\u1ee9c \\u0111\\u1ec3 c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng nhanh v\\u01a1i c&aacute;c t&aacute;c v\\u1ee5 c\\u01a1 b\\u1ea3n nh\\u01b0 g&otilde; v\\u0103n b\\u1ea3n, duy\\u1ec7t web&hellip;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">Tuy v\\u1eady, m\\u1eb7c d&ugrave; \\u0111&atilde; \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c trang b\\u1ecb m\\u1ed9t PCIe NVMe SSD &ndash; lo\\u1ea1i nhanh nh\\u1ea5t &ndash; \\u1ed5 Toshiba XG4 Dell \\u0111&atilde; khi\\u1ebfn cho m&aacute;y b\\u1ecb ch\\u1eadm v&agrave; l&agrave;m \\u0111i\\u1ec3m s\\u1ed1 c\\u1ee7a Precision 7720 b\\u1ecb th\\u1ea5p \\u0111i tr&ecirc;n m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 b&agrave;i ki\\u1ec3m tra. N\\u1ebfu b\\u1ea1n thay th\\u1ebf m\\u1ed9t 512GB PCIe Class 50 SSD th&igrave; 7720 s\\u1ebd nhanh h\\u01a1n.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">V\\u1edbi b&agrave;i ki\\u1ec3m tra hi\\u1ec7u su\\u1ea5t t\\u1ed5ng th\\u1ec3 Geekbench, Precision \\u0111\\u1ea1t 11,402 \\u0111i\\u1ec3m. Th\\u1ea5p h\\u01a1n so v\\u1edbi m\\u1ee9c trung b&igrave;nh c\\u1ee7a PC l&agrave; 15,883 \\u0111i\\u1ec3m hay nh\\u1eefng chi\\u1ebfc Mobile Workstation kh&aacute;c nh\\u01b0&nbsp;ZBook Studio (Xeon E3-1505M v5, 32GB RAM), 13.518 t\\u1eeb ThinkPad P70 (Xeon E3-1505M v5, RAM 16GB), MSI WE72 (Core i7-7700HQ, 32GB) v&agrave; 14702 t\\u1eeb Precision 5520 (Xeon E3-1505M v6, 32GB RAM).<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">N\\u1ebfu b\\u1ea1n mu\\u1ed1n l&agrave;m \\u0111\\u1ed3 h\\u1ecda 3D, Precision 7720 l\\u1ea1i l&agrave; l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c. V\\u1edbi GPU Nvidia Quadro P3000 v\\u1edbi 6GB, Precision 7720 \\u0111\\u1ea1t 2.143 \\u0111i\\u1ec3m th\\u1eed nghi\\u1ec7m 3DMark Fire Strike Ultra. T\\u1ed1t h\\u01a1n 825 \\u0111i\\u1ec3m so v\\u1edbi ZBook Studio (4GB Quadro M1000M), 1.856 t\\u1eeb ThinkPad P70 (4GB Quadro M4000M), 1.324 t\\u1eeb MSI WE72 7RJ (4GB Quadro M2200) v&agrave; 980 t\\u1eeb Precision 5520 (4GB Quadro M1200 ).<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\"><strong>PIN<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;\\\">Dell Precision 7720 c&oacute; th\\u1eddi l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng r\\u1ea5t t\\u1ed1t. Khi ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng v\\u1edbi c&aacute;c t&aacute;c v\\u1ee5 th&ocirc;ng th\\u01b0\\u1eddng, m&aacute;y \\u0111\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ebfn 9 gi\\u1edd 34 ph&uacute;t, d&agrave;i h\\u01a1n h\\u1eb3n so v\\u1edbi m\\u1ee9c trung b&igrave;nh l&agrave; 4 gi\\u1ed